9:45 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Beware Platone!</span><hr size=1> There is a low level iksar monk named Platone (obviously someone's alt) pulling the oldest and stupidest trick in the book. So there I was in EC, auctioning my heart out for the one item I would give my very soul for right now. A Blood Ember BP. When a low level player responded that he had one I was immediately skeptical, but being the uber item I wanted I went through the motions of getting a large sum of plat and Massive Dragonclaw Shard that we agreed to trade for it. Upon the trade time.. He tells me &quot;Oh I got the BE BP on my other character (my eyes roll to the back of my head) and I want the plat on this char... give me the plat and the item and I'll be right back with the BE BP&quot;. I couldn't believe what I was hearing. Do people still try this crap? Naturally I refused and when I did all hell broke lose. He begged and pleaded and called names until he said alright I will be back with my SK who has the item. Of course he never returned. Now I know that all of you are smart enough not to fall for such a stupid attempt at a scam but if you see Platone... don't hesitate to give him hell for this pathetic scam.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/usancta.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sancta</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 144<br> <font color=#E9D756>(7/6/01 4:11:00 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://wrathofthemonkeys.com/images/sancta.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Beware Platone!</span><hr size=1> That makes me sick.  I do that and I believe I am trusted by many of the players on this server as I have ALWAYS come back with the item.  I hate people who do this because it ruins it for those of us that actually DO TE RIGHT THING.  I remember doing this for you once upon a time Dorien...  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :rolleyes --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/eyes.gif ALT=":rolleyes"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p>Sancta Nox<br>The Tunarian Heirophant w/o a Home.<br><br> "Of the Many Truths select one... It will become a Falsehood and you a Fanatic"</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#575757><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ufystaen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fystaen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 50<br> <font color=#E9D756>(7/8/01 4:37:36 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Sancta</span><hr size=1> I would give a player items and cash if he said he was going to return with another item for me, except the person who wanted me to do this would have to be very well know to me. Sancta, I have never heard of you before, so if you came up and said &quot;I do this all the time, people know they can trust me on this server&quot; I sure as hell wouldn't do it for you :P<br>
